I suggest you to add this item directly in your toolbar tag with an ImageButton in the activity xml file. It&#39;ll be easier for you to manage click events and have full control.

For that you have to set a theme that has no action bar like this : Theme.MaterialComponents.Light.NoActionBar

                `&lt;androidx.appcompat.widget.Toolbar
